%h3= @resource.email_greeting

%p We received a request to reset your password for your account. 

%p No worries, we're here to assist you in regaining access. Follow the link below to reset your password:

%br
%table{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :role => "presentation", :width => "100%"}
  %tr
    %td{:align => "center"}
      = link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) , class: 'button'
%br
%p If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.
%p Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.
